---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Imprint — Adasight"
  description="Legal imprint and company information for Adasight B.V., registered in the Netherlands."
  canonicalPath="/imprint"
>

<!-- ═══════════════════ HERO ═══════════════════ -->
<section class="legal-hero">
  <div class="legal-hero-inner">
    <p class="label">// LEGAL</p>
    <h1>Imprint</h1>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════ CONTENT ═══════════════════ -->
<section class="legal-content">
  <div class="prose">

    <h2>Company Information</h2>

    <p><strong>Adasight B.V.</strong><br />
    Keurenplein 4, Unit G4481<br />
    1069CD Amsterdam<br />
    The Netherlands</p>

    <h3>Registration</h3>
    <p>Registered with the Netherlands Chamber of Commerce (KVK)<br />
    VAT Number: 864893176B01</p>

    <h3>Contact</h3>
    <p>Phone: <a href="tel:+31643679810">+31 643 67 98 10</a><br />
    Email: <a href="mailto:hello@adasight.com">hello@adasight.com</a><br />
    Website: <a href="https://www.adasight.com">https://www.adasight.com</a></p>

    <h3>Management</h3>
    <p>Dayana Marin -- Co-founder &amp; CEO<br />
    Gregor Spielmann -- Co-founder &amp; COO</p>

    <h3>Responsible for Content</h3>
    <p>Gregor Spielmann<br />
    Keurenplein 4, Unit G4481<br />
    1069CD Amsterdam<br />
    The Netherlands</p>

    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>

    <h3>Liability for Content</h3>
    <p>The contents of our pages were created with the utmost care. However, we cannot guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of the content. As a service provider, we are responsible for our own content on these pages under general law. However, we are not obligated to monitor transmitted or stored third-party information or to investigate circumstances that indicate illegal activity.</p>

    <h3>Liability for Links</h3>
    <p>Our website contains links to external third-party websites over whose content we have no influence. Therefore, we cannot accept any liability for this external content. The respective provider or operator of the linked pages is always responsible for the content of those pages. The linked pages were checked for possible legal violations at the time of linking. Illegal content was not identifiable at the time of linking.</p>

    <h3>Copyright</h3>
    <p>The content and works created by the site operators on these pages are subject to Dutch copyright law. Duplication, processing, distribution, and any kind of use beyond the limits of copyright law require the written consent of the respective author or creator. Downloads and copies of this site are only permitted for private, non-commercial use.</p>

    <h2>Data Protection</h2>
    <p>For information on how we handle your personal data, please refer to our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

  </div>
</section>

</Base>

<style>
  /* ─── Hero ─── */
  .legal-hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 10rem 2rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .legal-hero-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: .8125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: .08em;
    color: var(--cyan);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .legal-hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Red Hat Display', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  /* ─── Prose Content ─── */
  .legal-content {
    padding: 2rem 2rem 6rem;
  }
  .prose {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .prose h2 {
    font-family: 'Red Hat Display', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose h3 {
    font-family: 'Red Hat Display', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose a {
    color: var(--cyan);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .prose a:hover {
    color: #fff;
  }
  .prose strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .legal-hero { padding: 8rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
    .legal-content { padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 580px) {
    .legal-hero { padding: 7rem 1rem 2rem; }
    .legal-content { padding: 1.5rem 1rem 3rem; }
    .prose { font-size: 0.9375rem; }
  }
</style>
